snippet.title: Scott Pilgrim Versus (FULL MUGEN/IKEMEN GAME) Reveal !!!
snippet.description:
Scott Pilgrim is back again but this time EVERYONE IS HERE ! 

GET READY FOR THE NEXT BATTLE !

Scott and Friends prepare to duke it out yet again but this time its every man for themselves.

WHAT DO YOU FIGHT FOR ?
Love, Money, Fame, Vengeance, Power, Respect ?
or maybe you just love to fight.

SHATTER ALL EXPECTIOINS !!!

-Stay Ultra Fatal
